roteam1       = \n| majorwins      = \n| show-medals    = yes\n| medaltemplates = \n}}\n'''Jean Vidament''' (born 24 January 1944) is a French [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]].<ref name=\"CA\">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/coureurfiche.php?coureurid=16452 |title=Jean Vidament |accessdate=20 July 2017 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref> He rode in the [[1970 Tour de France]].<ref name=\"TDF\">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/ritfiche.php?ritid=131662 |title=Tour de France 1970 |accessdate=20 July 2017 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Cycling Archives|16452}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vidament, Jean}}\n[[Category:1944 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:French male cyclists]]\n[[Category:Tour de France cyclists]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n{{France-cycling-bio-1940s-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lugnuts", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Vidament"}
